These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, juice, 7up, almond-milk, fanta, sprite, coffee
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: july, february, november, september, december, march, august
7 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, cat, snake, goat, rabbit, bird, mouse
 1. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
 2. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in july##2
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is the owner of the mouse##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is between the owner of the goat and the person drinking fanta##2
 8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 9. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the person drinking coffee is the person who's birthday is in november##1
11. the person who's birthday is in march is the person drinking almond-milk##1
12. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
13. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's birthday is in december##1
14. the person drinking sprite is between the owner of the snake and the owner of the mouse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Beverage   | fanta | soy-milk     | sprite | juice | almond-milk | coffee  | 7up  |
| Birthday   | july  | september        | february  | august     | march   | november       | december   |
| Pet         | cat   | mouse | goat    | snake  | rabbit | bird | guinea-pig |

