.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
7 different pets are kept: mouse, pony, frog, lizard, goldfish, dog, bird
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: hip-hop, indie, metal, soul, classical, ambient, d&b
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, bluemaster, montecristo, bolivar, aristoff, fonseca, baccarat
 1. the owner of the pony is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 2. the fan classical is the fan classical##1
 3. the fan classical is on the right of the fan soul##1
 4. the fan soul is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
 5. the fan hip-hop is the owner of the bird##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is the bolivar-smoker##1
 7. the owner of the mouse is between the fan d&b and the baccarat-smoker##2
 8. the fan metal is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 9. the fan d&b is on the left of the fan soul##1
10. the owner of the frog is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
11. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
12. the dunhill-smoker is the owner of the pony##1
13. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
14. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
15. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
16. the fan indie is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Pet   | dog | bird      | lizard     | mouse  | goldfish | frog | pony |
| Music-Genre         | indie  | hip-hop | ambient | metal | d&b | soul   | classical  |
