 7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 8. the person watching zombie movies is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 9. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
10. the person watching crime movies is the person traveling to berlin##1
11. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
12. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in july##2
13. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
14. the person watching horror movies is the person traveling to rome##1
15. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
