There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, hot-chocolate, sprite, mirinda, almond-milk, cola
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
