 4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the tower house##1
 6. the townhouse house is in the middle##1
 7. the cottage house is the person who's hobby is chess##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 9. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person drinking iced-tea##1
10. the futuristic house is the person drinking mirinda##1
11. the tower house is on the right of the modern house##1
12. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the art-deco house##1
13. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
